<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Geeks Of London</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/screen.css" type="text/css" media="screen" title="stylesheet" charset="utf-8">
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
        <div class='wrapper'>
            <a href='/'><img src="/images/logo.png" /></a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>
        <div class='wrapper'>
			<form method="post" action="/update/<%= @subscription['email'] %>">
            	<div class='content'>
	                <h1>Hi <%= @subscription['first_name'] unless @subscription['first_name'].nil? %>,</h1>
	                <p>Below you will find the different types of email we send to <%= @subscription['email'] %>, all you need to do is check or uncheck the boxes next to each one.</p>
	                <p>Finally if you want to leave us, you can click the unsubscribe link at the bottom.</p>
	                <p class="signoff">Your Geeks of London Team</p>
	            </div>
	            <hr>
	            <div class="interest odd">
	                <h3>BarCamp</h3>
	                <p>You will receive emails about BarCamp type events including announcements, ticket releases etc.</p>
	                Yes I want to receive these: <input type="checkbox" value="TRUE" name="barcamp" <%= @subscription['barcamp'] %>>
	            </div>
	            <div class="interest">
	                <h3>Hack Days</h3>
	                <p>You will receive emails about Hack Day type events including announcements, ticket releases etc.</p>
	                Yes I want to receive these: <input type="checkbox" value="TRUE" name="hack" <%= @subscription['hack'] %>>               
	            </div>
	            <div class="interest odd">
	                <h3>Anything Else</h3>
	                <p>You will receive emails about other events we are running, involved in or attending.</p>
	                Yes I want to receive these: <input type="checkbox" value="TRUE" name="geek" <%= @subscription['anything'] %>>
	            </div>
	            <hr>
	            <div class='content'>
	                <h3>Our Commitments to you</h3>
	                <ul class="commitments">
	                    <li>Only one marketing email per week per interest.</li>
	                    <li>Never share email address with anyone.</li>
	                    <li>We will unsubscribe you as soon as you ask us.</li>
	                    <li>Free cake if you get an email you didn't ask for at our next event.</li>
	                </ul>
	                <br>
	                <p>Finally the above is not legally binding but we will try really hard to live up-to it.</p>
	            </div>
	            <hr>
	            <input type="submit" value="Update my details" class="update_button" />
	            <div class="unsubscribe">
	                <a href="#" class="unsubscribe">I have had enough emails and I want to cancel everything.</a>
	            </div>
			</form>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class='wrapper'>
            <a href='http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/'>Some rights reserved</a>
        </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
